      "paragraphs": [
        {
          "sentences": [
            {
              "text": "Leo and Mia were students who loved to visit the local library after school.",
              "audioStart": 0.1,
              "audioEnd": 4
            },
            {
              "text": "One rainy afternoon, they found an old, dusty book which contained a hidden mountain map.",
              "audioStart": 4.862,
              "audioEnd": 9.488
            },
            {
              "text": "The map showed a secret cave that was located high in the mountains.",
              "audioStart": 10.35,
              "audioEnd": 13.65
            },
            {
              "text": "It had been placed there by someone many years ago.",
              "audioStart": 14.512,
              "audioEnd": 16.988
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "sentences": [
            {
              "text": "They knew that they should find the cave before the sun went down.",
              "audioStart": 17.85,
              "audioEnd": 20.85
            },
            {
              "text": "If they arrived late, it would be impossible to see the path.",
              "audioStart": 21.712,
              "audioEnd": 24.825
            },
            {
              "text": "They walked quickly through the forest and climbed the steep mountain.",
              "audioStart": 25.688,
              "audioEnd": 28.788
            },
            {
              "text": "Leo and Mia were excited because they felt like real explorers.",
              "audioStart": 29.65,
              "audioEnd": 33.05
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "sentences": [
            {
              "text": "The mountain was very high, but they continued to climb with great care.",
              "audioStart": 33.913,
              "audioEnd": 37.562
            },
            {
              "text": "As they went higher, the air became cold and the light began to fade.",
              "audioStart": 38.425,
              "audioEnd": 42.163
            },
            {
              "text": "They could see a small, dark opening that was hidden behind a large tree.",
              "audioStart": 43.025,
              "audioEnd": 46.7
            },
            {
              "text": "It seemed that this was the entrance to the secret cave.",
              "audioStart": 47.562,
              "audioEnd": 50.225
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "sentences": [
            {
              "text": "Leo moved the branches aside so that they could enter the dark space.",
              "audioStart": 51.087,
              "audioEnd": 54.475
            },
            {
              "text": "Inside the cave, there was a small box which had been left on the ground.",
              "audioStart": 55.337,
              "audioEnd": 59.05
            },
            {
              "text": "They opened the box and saw that it contained ancient coins and a letter.",
              "audioStart": 59.913,
              "audioEnd": 63.425
            },
            {
              "text": "The letter was written by a man who had lived there long ago.",
              "audioStart": 64.287,
              "audioEnd": 67.025
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "sentences": [
            {
              "text": "They read the letter and learned that the treasure was meant for brave people.",
              "audioStart": 67.888,
              "audioEnd": 71.162
            },
            {
              "text": "If they had not followed the map, they would never have found this place.",
              "audioStart": 72.025,
              "audioEnd": 75.412
            },
            {
              "text": "The sun was almost down, so they decided to return home with the treasure.",
              "audioStart": 76.275,
              "audioEnd": 80.05
            },
            {
              "text": "They were very happy because they had finished their great adventure.",
              "audioStart": 80.912,
              "audioEnd": 83.987
            }
          ]
        }
